    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. GCI below 5%, NIH predictions within experimental uncertainty, and direct QoI alignment with COU decision metric collectively support acceptance. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
